data.description: * IN-LAW SUITE * Perfect for guests or game room! Spacious bedrooms inside, screened lanai for entertaining and relaxing outside. Fenced back yard. LOW HOA. Built-in SURROUND SOUND. Tastefully landscaped and tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac with minimal traffic, it offers modern updates and functional living. HGTV-inspired decor. NEW GRANITE COUNTERTOPS. Abundant counter space and cabinets. Experience the convenience of a LAUNDRY SHOOT on the second floor. See for yourself to discover the secret door! Not a subdivision; it's a lifestyle. Community amenities: pool, soccer, baseball, and football fields, & playgrounds! Just minutes from I-95 and 295, Greenland Park and the hub of shopping and entertainment at St. Johns Town Center...Interior has been FRESHLY PAINTED** Love to boat or fish then you will only be 20 minutes from Julington Creek Fish Camp and Freedom Boat Club. Love to golf then TPC Sawgrass and the beaches are only 30 minutes down the road.
